    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Pointing your index finger at a creature in range, you generate a spark of yellow chakra, which summons six thin, wide beams of seals that slam into their midsection and hold them in place.</p><p>The target must make a Dexterity saving throw. On a failed save, they are unable to move any part of their body, including the parts not struck by the beams. They are restrained and incapacitated for the duration. At the end of their turn, they can remake the save to end both conditions.</p>",
